title: DBZ Abridged Episodes 1-44 + Movies (TFS)
description:
All episodes and movies up until 10/26/2014. Same quality as on Youtube, files are MP4.

TeamFourStar does great things with the Dragonball Z series, cutting the original episodes into more manageable chunks, removing 95% of the filler and rewriting the script into something truly awesome. The voice acting exceeds that of the original series in almost every instance, and the jokes come at a strenuous pace, ranging from poking fun at the writing of the original series in both blatantly obvious and cleverly subtle ways to running gags that really do get funnier with every telling to mocking those characters of little worth that seem to plague the series. The characters are all extreme reflections of their original-series counterparts, but they're well-thought out and fit this series perfectly. If you're a fan of the original series, then this is one for you. If you're not a fan because you're seen it and it's ridiculously tedious most of the time, then you still may want to check this one out. Enjoy.

My first torrent on here, hope it works right. Good luck, and rock on TFS!
